-and-in-gaza-they-didnt-deserve-to-die/0000018b-bfcf-d03e-a3ab-bfffe07d0000</link><description>在目前席卷以色列的法西斯现实中，即使是这样的声明也被视为叛国和对以色列仇恨的表达。你怎么敢比较？</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 22:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-12/ty-article/.premium/in-both-israel-and-in-gaza-they-didnt-deserve-to-die/0000018b-bfcf-d03e-a3ab-bfffe07d0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列军队接近加沙的希法时，医院警告将倒塌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-11/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-troops-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-warns-of-collapse/0000018b-bfcd-d03e-a3ab-bffd319a0000</link><description>以色列国防军消息人士称，以色列军方在过去几天联系了希法的负责人，警告他撤离</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 20:32:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-11/ty-article/.premium/as-israeli-troops-near-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-warns-of-collapse/0000018b-bfcd-d03e-a3ab-bffd319a0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉要求美国施压，迫使以色列停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-11-11/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-leader-nasrallah-demands-pressure-on-u-s-to-force-cease-fire-on-israel/0000018b-bf0c-dedf-adab-ff1cf37b0000</link><description>哈桑·纳斯鲁拉在加沙战争爆发以来的第二次公开演讲中呼吁阿拉伯和伊斯兰峰会上的国家进行外交干预 ■ 以色列国防部长加兰特：“我们在加沙所做的，我们知道在贝鲁特如何做”</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 16:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2023-11-11/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-leader-nasrallah-demands-pressure-on-u-s-to-force-cease-fire-on-israel/0000018b-bf0c-dedf-adab-ff1cf37b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人集会呼吁释放哈马斯人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-11/ty-article/israelis-to-rally-across-country-to-call-for-release-of-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/0000018b-beed-dea2-a9bf-feffdd480000</link><description>“我已经受够了拥抱和言语，我想要行动。奥利·吉尔博亚 (Orly Gilboa) 19 岁的女儿丹妮拉 (Daniella) 被扣为人质，在特拉维夫说道：“现在就把我的女儿带回家吧。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 15:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-11/ty-article/israelis-to-rally-across-country-to-call-for-release-of-hostages-from-hamas-captivity/0000018b-beed-dea2-a9bf-feffdd480000</guid></item><item><title>麻省理工学院解释为什么没有暂停威胁犹太人的亲巴勒斯坦学生：“签证问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-11/ty-article/.premium/mit-on-why-it-didnt-suspend-pro-palestinians-students-threatening-jews-visa-issues/0000018b-be9b-df42-a78f-bfdb51c00000</link><description>根据“麻省理工学院以色列联盟及其支持者”组织的一份声明，组织抗议活动的“反对种族隔离委员会”组织的学生多次骚扰麻省理工学院的教职员工和学生，因为他们是犹太人。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 13:52:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-11/ty-article/.premium/mit-on-why-it-didnt-suspend-pro-palestinians-students-threatening-jews-visa-issues/0000018b-be9b-df42-a78f-bfdb51c00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人集会敦促政府释放人质；以色列国防军：哈马斯失去对加沙地带北部的控制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-11/ty-article-live/israeli-army-fights-hamas-inside-gaza-city-denies-airstrike-against-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-bc72-dea2-a9bf-fcfef8b30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：在任何情况下我都不会同意放弃对加沙地带的安全控制 ■ 沙特阿拉伯峰会上的阿拉伯领导人呼吁停止加沙战斗 ■ 报道：以色列国防军包围了加沙三所医院，要求 Al-Shifa 主任疏散所有患者 ■以色列高级官员：“人质可能被扣押在希法医院” ■ 至少 1,200 名以色列人在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生，239 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯管理的加沙卫生部：自战斗开始以来，已有 11,078 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 03:51:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-11/ty-article-live/israeli-army-fights-hamas-inside-gaza-city-denies-airstrike-against-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-bc72-dea2-a9bf-fcfef8b30000</guid></item><item><title>贝埃里的美术馆被哈马斯摧毁。它的策展人幸存下来并讲述其独特的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-11/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/beeris-art-gallery-was-destroyed-by-hamas-its-curators-survived-to-tell-its-unique-tale/0000018b-b9b1-df42-a78f-bdf3eec60000</link><description>艺术家兼策展人齐瓦·杰林 (Ziva Jelin) 和索菲·贝尔宗·麦基 (Sofie Berzon MacKie) 在贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 经营着一家画廊，展出了与该地区有联系的著名艺术家的作品。 10 月 7 日的哈马斯大屠杀摧毁了他们毕生的心血。现在，回顾过去的展览，几乎每一件作品都似乎体现着一个致命的预言</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Nov 2023 00:33:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-11/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/beeris-art-gallery-was-destroyed-by-hamas-its-curators-survived-to-tell-its-unique-tale/0000018b-b9b1-df42-a78f-bdf3eec60000</guid></item></channel></rss>